entry.title: SNOWFALL WARNING , Killarney
entry.summary: Persons in or near this area should be on the lookout for adverse weather conditions and take necessary safety precautions. Issued: 05:33 AM EDT Saturday 25 March 2023

entry.title: Saturday: Snow at times heavy mixed with ice pellets. High plus 1.
entry.summary: Becoming cloudy this morning then snow at times heavy. Snow mixed with ice pellets and rain late this afternoon. Local blowing snow this afternoon. Snow and ice pellet amount 10 cm. Wind east 20 km/h increasing to 40 gusting to 60 late this morning. High plus 1. Wind chill minus 9 this morning. UV index 1 or low. Forecast issued 05:30 AM EDT Saturday 25 March 2023

entry.title: Saturday night: Periods of snow mixed with rain. Low minus 1.
entry.summary: Periods of snow. Snow at times mixed with rain this evening. Local blowing snow overnight. Snowfall amount 5 cm. Wind northeast 30 km/h gusting to 50 becoming west 30 gusting to 50 near midnight. Low minus 1. Wind chill minus 8 overnight. Forecast issued 05:30 AM EDT Saturday 25 March 2023
